title: Give Me Something To Break (feat. Jessimae Peluso)
description:
After watching the new HBO Max documentary on Woodstock 1999 the guys take callers who were at the infamous festival. Jessimae Peluso joins the show and tells the gang about her new show Tattoo Redo. Dan decides he wants Pete Davidson to play Kid Rock in his biopic.
